  "notes": "The root div always carries 'paragraph' and 'paragraph--view-mode--default' classes in addition to 'paragraph--type--para-signpost-box'. The 'dark' and 'highlight' modifiers are mutually exclusive in practice. The image block uses a responsive picture element but the component stores a single src for the fallback img tag. The title block always contains a .sbtitle div and a .sbarrow div with a Font Awesome arrow icon — both are always rendered. The aria-label on the anchor mirrors the title text in all observed samples.",
